This file lists user visible changes that were made between releases.  For
more verbose descriptions of these and internal changes see the ChangeLog
files.

Version 0.0.16
--------------

 * fixed documentation of conductor losses in coax line
 * updates in the "measurement expressions" chapter of the workbook

Version 0.0.15
--------------

 * new report about Verilog-A photodiode model
 * new report about Verilog-A EPFL-EKV v2.6 model

Version 0.0.14
--------------

 * new report about the Verilog-A MESFET models
 * new report about Potentiometer model in Verilog-A
 * new report about the Verilog-A Logarithmic Amplifier

Version 0.0.13
--------------

 * new report about the Verilog-A Modular OpAmp
 * fixed harmonic balance descriptions

Version 0.0.12
--------------

 * report about Curtice Level 1 MESFET modelling
 * new tutorial about component, compact device and circuit modelling
   using symbolic equations
 * added new ReportBook including Verilog-AMS interface description
   and the SPICE to Qucs conversion test files
 * finished documentation about Singular Value Decomposition
 * finished introductory tutorial

Version 0.0.11
--------------

 * new introductory tutorial started
 * added small section about AC analysis
 * tutorial update about operational amplifier modelling
 * tutorial about simulation of SPICE netlists
 * new tutorial about modelling the 555 timer
 * documented excess phase implementation for BJTs

Version 0.0.10
--------------

 * new tutorial about modelling operational amplifiers
 * documentation of the singular value decomposition
 * new reference handbook chapter about measurement expressions

Version 0.0.9
-------------

 * added description of how to simulate components defined in the frequency
   domain in the time domain
 * improved and fixed description of the harmonic balance
 * tutorial: mixed signal simulations using gate components
 * tutorial: introduction into digital simulations using FreeHDL

Version 0.0.8
-------------

 * first available version
